Executive Profile
Hugh R. Rovit  Chief Executive Officer, Sure Fit Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 4 Board Members in 4 different organizations across 8 different industries.See Board Relationships57--
Background

		Mr. Hugh R. Rovit has been the Chief Executive Officer of Sure Fit Inc. since 2006. Mr. Rovit was a Principal in Masson & Company, LLC from 2001 to 2005. He served as the Chief Financial Officer and Chief Operating Officer of Best Textiles Acquisition, LLC (Alternate names, Best Manufacturing Group LLC and Best Manufacturing Inc.) from 1998 to 2001. Mr. Rovit served as Chief Financial Officer of Royce Hosiery Mills Inc. from 1991 to 1998. He served as Assistant to the ... Chairman of The Natori Company Inc., a manufacturer of intimate apparel and accessories, from 1988 to 1991 and Analyst and Associate with Lehman Brothers from 1983 to 1985 and 1985 to 1987, respectively. Mr. Rovit served as Chairman of the Board of Atkins Nutritionals, Inc. after its emergence from bankruptcy in January 2006. He has been a Director of Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc. since June 2010. He serves as a Director of Cosmetics Essence, Inc. and SB/RH Holdings, LLC. He has been a Director of Oneida Ltd. since October 25, 2004. Mr. Rovit is a director of certain affiliates of Laminar. He has been a Director of Nellson Nutraceutical, LLC since March 2008. He served as a Director of Spectrum Brands, Inc. from August 2009 to October 2010 and Kid Brands, Inc. from July 2010 to July 18, 2013. Mr. Rovit served as a Director of Atkins Nutritionals, Inc. since February 2006. Mr. Rovit earned a Bachelor of Arts degree with distinction in government from Dartmouth College and an M.B.A. degree from Harvard Business School.Read Full Background




