Insider Activity


Individual




Hugh R. Rovit



Mr. Hugh R. Rovit is Independent Director at Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc. and SB/RH Holdings LLC. Mr. Rovit was previously employed as Independent Director by Kid Brands, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Sure Fit, Inc., Chairman by Atkins Nutritionals, Inc., Director-Emeritus by Oneida Ltd., a Principal by Masson & Co. LLC, Chief Financial Officer by Best Manufacturing, Inc., Chief Financial Officer by Royce Hosiery Mills, Inc., Chief Financial Officer by Best Manufacturing Group LLC, Director-Emeritus by Cosmetic Essence LLC, and Chief Executive Officer by Ellery Homestyles LLC. He also served on the board at Spectrum Brands, Inc. and Nellson Nutraceutical LLC. He received his undergraduate degree from Dartmouth College and an MBA from Harvard Business School.



